Sheldon Renan:

"Nick Carr talks on video about the importance of ethics (and making ethical
decisions about shaping infrastructure going forward) at
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w53IEvKawVE.
The video provided a surprise opening for all of us who attended GigaOm's
Structure 08 Conference in San Francisco last Wednesday (June 25.)

Om Malik on stage introduced Carr on video. Content: the radical  changes
that lie ahead with cloud computing, the new infrastructure, the need to
include ethics in the process of planning the future of infrastructure. Net
net: 5 minutes and 41 seconds of thought-provoking video."


